<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/christian-wakeford> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Christian Wakeford was appointed Junior Lord of the Treasury (Government Whip) on 7 September 2025. He was previously Assistant Whip, House of Commons between 10 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Bury South in July 2024."@en .
